At the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 13 people and 4 households residing in the town. The population density was {{convert|20.97|PD/sqmi|PD/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. There were 70 housing units at an average density of {{convert|112.90|/sqmi|/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. The racial composition of the city was: 84.62% [[White (U.S. Census)|White]], 0.077% [[Hispanic (U.S. Census)|Hispanic]] or [[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Latino American]], and 0.077% Native American.<ref>{{cite web |title=Explore Census Data |url=https://data.census.gov/profile/Fontana_Dam_town,_North_Carolina?g=160XX00US3723980 |website=data.census.gov |access-date=January 15, 2024}}</ref>

